e xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ybr1665702721823.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ybr1665702721823.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ybr1665702721823.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ybr1665702721823\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Change the <code class=\"ph codeph\">init</code> option in the device translation table.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__topic_d140180e1_d140181e1_d140182e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__p_d140183e1_d140184e1_d140185e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$DISPLAY_INIT</code> = <var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__section_gbh_llq_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1024591e65\"> Options </h2>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__section_mtk_lmq_bwb\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Options Available with <code class=\"ph codeph\">init</code> and $DISPLAY_INIT</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\nOption\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\nDescription\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n0 or setting not mentioned\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\nCauses all video attributes to be reinitialized\nat the end of a display.\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n1\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Same as 0, but specifies the\n                        display as a stratus v102 display. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n2\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Same as 0, but specifies the\n                        display as an HP terminal. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n3\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\nSame as 0, but specifies the display\nas an HP terminal.\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n4\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ybr1665702721823__d7258e17__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Allows video attributes to be\n                        initialized just before the next display, instead of at the end of the\n                        previous display. Also, the initialization will not occur when the cursor is\n                        already on the correct position for the next display and the attributes are\n                        equal to the incoming video attributes. This provides better performance\n                        than the options 1 through 3. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__section_qll_llq_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1024591e150\">Defaults </h2>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__section_yt4_mmq_bwb\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__table_d16646e1_d16647e1_d16648e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> client assignment files </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> [SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__section_edq_llq_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1024591e200\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__p_d140195e1_d140196e1_d140197e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DISPLAY_INIT</span> allows you to change the <code class=\"ph codeph\">init</code> option of\n        the device translation table without creating a new device translation table. The possible\n        values for <var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var> are shown in the following table. If\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DISPLAY_INIT</span> is not mentioned, the default setting is\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__section_ik5_llq_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle exampletitle\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__p_d140198e1_d140199e1_d140200e1\"> Example: $DISPLAY_INIT </h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ybr1665702721823__pre_tpw_4mq_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$DISPLAY_INIT = 4</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/voi1705662348184.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Device Translation Tables</a><p>Device translation tables handle output to screens and printers. They map Uniface logical functions onto device functions, making it possible for Uniface to support a wide variety of hardware platforms, including their output devices.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dcn1665702982352.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Session Mnemonics</a><p>These mnemonics start and end a session.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534022\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534022\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$DISPLAY_INIT Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Change the init option in the device translation table. $DISPLAY_INIT = Option Options Table 1. Options Available with init and $DISPLAY_INIT Option Description 0 or setting not mentioned Causes all video attributes to be reinitialized at the end of a display. 1 Same as 0, but specifies the display as a stratus v102 display. 2 Same as 0, but specifies the display as an HP terminal. 3 Same as 0, but specifies the display as an HP terminal. 4 Allows video attributes to be initialized just before the next display, instead of at the end of the previous display. Also, the initialization will not occur when the cursor is already on the correct position for the next display and the attributes are equal to the incoming video attributes. This provides better performance than the options 1 through 3. Defaults Assignment file: client assignment files Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description $DISPLAY_INIT allows you to change the init option of the device translation table without creating a new device translation table. The possible values for Option are shown in the following table. If $DISPLAY_INIT is not mentioned, the default setting is 0 . Example: $DISPLAY_INIT $DISPLAY_INIT = 4 Copy Related Links Device Translation Tables Device translation tables handle output to screens and printers. They map Uniface logical functions onto device functions, making it possible for Uniface to support a wide variety of hardware platforms, including their output devices. Session Mnemonics These mnemonics start and end a session. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}